06:28.222 --> 06:29.721
So good.

06:29.723 --> 06:31.323
Ah.

06:31.325 --> 06:33.759
Skunky as hell, but just...
I love it, I don't care.

06:33.761 --> 06:34.826
Beer,

06:34.828 --> 06:36.828
