06:36.830 --> 06:38.830
Yeah, she is, yeah.

06:38.832 --> 06:42.667
So, Pat, you, uh,
you always been a seaman?

06:42.669 --> 06:44.703
Uh, by that I mean, a sailor.

06:44.705 --> 06:47.172
