06:47.174 --> 06:48.940
No, I got, I got ya, I got...

06:48.942 --> 06:51.676
No, I haven't, but you know,
since the virus hit,

06:51.678 --> 06:52.944
I said, Pat,

06:52.946 --> 06:55.447
what better excuse
to buy a boat?

06:55.449 --> 06:57.783
So then you just
came out here, huh?

06:57.785 --> 06:59.050
Oh, hightailed it.

06:59.052 --> 07:00.852
Yeah, kept my distance.

07:00.854 --> 07:02.387
Listened to the news

07:02.389 --> 07:05.090
