to this little lady...

07:13.299 --> 07:15.233
<i>...Deez Knots.</i>

07:15.235 --> 07:16.568
MIKE:
<i>Deez Knots,</i> I get it.

07:16.570 --> 07:18.537
Played my cards right.

07:18.539 --> 07:20.605
That virus hasn't
taken me down, yet.

07:20.607 --> 07:22.741
