07:22.743 --> 07:24.876
Nobody's immune, Mike.

07:27.613 --> 07:32.751
You know, sometimes I'll...
I'll anchor offshore at night.

07:32.753 --> 07:35.921
Big cities. Miami. New York.

07:35.923 --> 07:37.456
New Orleans.

07:37.458 --> 07:40.826
