07:59.412 --> 08:02.814
No, they're... they're...
they're not, technically, black.

08:02.816 --> 08:04.149
No, they're, you know,

08:04.151 --> 08:05.984
it's actually the absence
of color.

08:05.986 --> 08:09.087
