and my brother are in Tucson.

08:44.825 --> 08:46.458
Were.

08:47.460 --> 08:49.127
Yeah. Yeah, right, uh, were.

08:49.129 --> 08:50.795
Yeah.
Yeah.

08:50.797 --> 08:52.464
